==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Seasickness
<hw>Sea"sick`ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The peculiar sickness,
characterized by nausea and prostration, which is caused by the pitching
or rolling of a vessel.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Seaside</ent>⟦br⟧
